<div class="col five-sm clear">
<h2 id="section-top">Overview</h2>
</div>
<div class="col four-sm">
</div>
<div class="col three-sm" id="ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_PlaceHolderMain_contentColumn1">
<div class="panel">
<div class="panel-content">
<div class="pad clear">
<div id="imageContentf54162ba68fb4cc29d111eae8e9f6340">
<div class="profile-pic">
<img alt="BMI The Alexandra Hospital" border="0" id="ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_PlaceHolderMain_column1Content_column1Content_SummaryAndPhotoModule_PhotoView_DisplayImage" src="/Services/UserControls/UploadHandlers/MediaServerHandler.ashx?id=115894"/>
</div>
</div>
<p><strong>BMI The Alexandra Hospital in Cheadle, Cheshire</strong></p>
<p><a href="https://www.bmihealthcare.co.uk/hospitals/bmi-the-alexandra-hospital" target="_blank">BMI The Alexandra Hospital</a> in Cheadle, Cheshire has seven theatres, two endoscopy suites, a day care unit and a 12 bedded critical care unit.</p>
<p>We also treat NHS funded patients, and patients who wish to pay for their own treatment. To see which treatments are available for NHS funded patients, please take a look at the NHS Patients page.</p>
<p>Here is a list of some of the treatments available at <strong>BMI The Alexandra Hospital:</strong></p>
<p><strong><a href="https://www.bmihealthcare.co.uk/hospitals/bmi-the-alexandra-hospital/orthopaedics" target="_blank" title="Private Orthopaedic Treatment in Cheshire">Private Orthopaedic Treatment in Cheshire</a></strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Arthroscopy for wrist, elbow and shoulder</li>
<li>Trigger finger treatment</li>
<li>Arthroscopy for ankle and knee and hip</li>
<li>ACL reconstruction surgery</li>
<li><a href="https://www.bmihealthcare.co.uk/hospitals/bmi-the-alexandra-hospital/physiotherapy" target="_blank" title="Physiotherapy The Alexandra Hospital">Physiotherapy</a></li>
<li>Spinal surgery</li>
</ul>
<p><strong><a href="https://www.bmihealthcare.co.uk/treatments/imaging-and-radiology" target="_blank" title="Diagnostics and Imaging treatments in Cheshire">Diagnostics &amp; Imaging Treatments in Cheshire</a></strong></p>
<ul>
<li>CT scanning</li>
<li>MRI scan</li>
<li>Ultrasound</li>
<li>X-ray</li>
</ul>
<p><strong><a href="https://www.bmihealthcare.co.uk/treatments/fertility" target="_blank" title="Private fertility treatment in Cheshire">Private Fertility Treatment in Cheshire</a></strong></p>
<ul>
<li>IVF</li>
<li>Assisted hatching</li>
<li>Cycle monitoring</li>
<li>Embryo cryopreservation</li>
</ul>
<p><strong><a href="https://www.bmihealthcare.co.uk/treatments/cosmetic-surgery" target="_blank" title="Cosmetic Surgery Treatment in Cheshire">Cosmetic Surgery Treatment in Cheshire</a></strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Cosmetic surgery</li>
<li><a href="https://www.bmihealthcare.co.uk/hospitals/bmi-the-alexandra-hospital/varicose-veins-services" target="_blank" title="Vascular surgery in Cheshire">Vascular surgery</a></li>
</ul>
<p><strong><a href="https://www.bmihealthcare.co.uk/hospitals/bmi-the-alexandra-hospital/cardiac-services" target="_blank" title="Private cardiac services in Cheshire">Private Cardiac Services in Cheshire</a></strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Electrocardiogram (ECG) </li>
<li>Seven day ECG monitoring</li>
<li>Coronary angiography </li>
<li>Angioplasty </li>
<li>Implantable Defibrillator</li>
</ul>
<div><strong><a href="https://www.bmihealthcare.co.uk/treatments/general-medicine/general-medical-admission" target="_blank" title="General Medical Association">General Medical Association</a></strong></div>
<ul>
</ul>
<ul>
</ul>
<p>BMI Healthcare offer the best <a href="https://www.bmihealthcare.co.uk/patient-information/quality-of-care" target="_blank" title="Quality of care">quality of care</a> and services. For more information about our hospitals and services please visit the <a href="https://www.bmihealthcare.co.uk/" target="_blank" title="BMI Healthcare">website.</a></p></div>
</div>
</div>
