<h4 id="Article-51666">Making healthcare affordable - paying for yourself</h4>
<div id="imageContent434df7ce81e945c7b4b6cbff76196b65">
<div class="profile-pic">
<img alt="Pay for yourself with a BMI card" border="0" id="ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_PlaceHolderMain_column1Content_column1Content_ArticleListModule_ArticlesRepeater_ctl00_ctl00_ArticleImage_DisplayImage" src="/Services/UserControls/UploadHandlers/MediaServerHandler.ashx?id=36736"/>
</div>
</div>
<p>If you are facing a long wait for the diagnosis or operation you need, or if specialist treatment is no longer available through the NHS in your area, you can choose to pay for treatment yourself. The BMI Card is a unique credit card that allows you to spread the cost of healthcare.  <a href="http://www.bmihealthcare.co.uk/paying-for-yourself-0001" target="_blank">Click here to find out more.</a></p>
<p class="last-updated">Last updated on 24 November 2015.</p>
